Notes: Terry Porter Tipoff Classic Game 2...SP advances to play Upper Iowa Sat. at
3 pm in title game...LU will face Marian (Ind.) for consolation at 1 pm...SP
jumped out to 18-0 lead over first 9:45 of game...LU scored first seven points
of second half and trailed 57-36 before 22-1 SP run for 79-37 lead.
